Name: ⚠️ Mandatory Fields Check
Description: Check if mandatory fields like email are populated.

Name: ✅ Data Completeness Check
Description: Verify the total number of rows in source matches target after ETL.

Name: 🔧 Transformation Logic Check
Description: Validate name transformation rule: first + last = full_name.

Name: 🔁 Duplicate Records Validation
Description: Ensure no duplicate customer_id present in source table.

Name: 🔎 Missing Records After ETL
Description: Ensure no missing rows between source and target after ETL.
